    {
      "type": "Question Dependencies",
      "text": "This question only appears if you select \"Yes\" in response to 7.33.",
      "typeKo": "문항 의존성",
      "textKo": "이 문항 만 표시됨 만약 귀사 선택 \"예\" 응답 7.33."
    },
    {
      "type": "Requested Content",
      "text": "General \nIf applicable, you should disclose the transmission and/or distribution related information from both your subsidiaries who are solely transmission and/or distribution and subsidiaries who provide both generation and transmission and/or distribution. \nCountry/area (column 1) \nSelect from the drop-down list the country/area in which your organization has transmission and distribution (T&D) activities. \nAnnual energy losses (% of annual load) (column 4) \nThis figure provides a measure of the power dissipated in the form of useless heat through the grid.\nScope where emissions from energy losses are accounted for (column 5) \nThe \"Scope 2 (market-based)\" dropdown only appears if you select if \"We are reporting a Scope 2, market-based figure\" in column \"Scope 2, market-based\" of 7.3.\nIn markets where the utility owns the generation assets and the T&D infrastructure, the utility would account for T&D losses in Scope 1. If the utility is a separate entity from power generating assets, the emissions from T&D losses would fall under Scope 2. \nEmissions from energy losses (metric tons CO2e) (column 6) \nNegative numbers are not allowed as reporting needs to be gross, not net figures. \nEmission figures should be for the reporting year only. \nFor further information, please see GHG Protocol Scope 2 Guidance . \nLength of network (km) (column 7) \nLength of network (km) is the total length of the routes, not cables, between different points of the network in kilometers. \nNumber of connections (column 8) \nThis is the number of connections in the network, either at supply side or delivery point and interconnections. \nArea covered (km2) (column 9) \nThis is the area serviced by the transmission or distribution network, expressed in kilometer squared.",
      "typeKo": "요청 내용",
      "textKo": "이 섹션은 해당 문항에서 CDP가 요청하는 작성 내용을 설명합니다. 위 응답방법, 열 구조, 드롭다운 선택지를 기준으로 보고연도와 조직 범위에 맞는 정보를 입력하십시오."
    },
    {
      "type": "Explanation of Terms",
      "text": "Annual load (also known as \"System load\") : the annual electricity delivered to the grid system by generating units expressed in GWh.\nTransmission and distribution losses (also known as \"Technical losses\") : the difference between system load and energy delivered to distribution grids/consumer, expressed as a percentage per energy delivered to the grid.",
      "typeKo": "용어 설명",
      "textKo": "이 섹션은 문항에서 사용하는 주요 용어의 의미를 설명합니다. 용어 해석은 CDP 2026 원문과 국문 양식의 용어 사용을 우선 적용하십시오."
    }
  ],
